prompt_zh:
按照要求输出<A>和<B>之间的对话。

## 对话要求:
1.说话人<B>的人格:{user_persona}
2.说话人<B>的处境:{user_situation}
3.说话人<A>的人格:{ai_persona}
4. At least 10-15 Rounds.
5. 对话格式:<Round X>
<B>: B的说话内容
<A>: A的说话内容

## 对话:

prompt_en:
The conversation between [A] and [B]. [A] and [B] comply with the following control information. According to the control information, {flag} initiates the conversation.

## [A] persona:
{ai_persona}

## [B] persona:
{user_persona}

## [B] situation:
{user_situation}

